headline: Assessing Cummins (CMI) Valuation After Record Results And New Clean-Tech Milestones
summary: Fresh catalysts for Cummins stock Cummins (CMI) is back in focus after record distribution segment revenue, an EPA green light for dual fuel adaptations on its X15 engines, and a US$2.1 million grant for hybrid haul truck systems. See our latest analysis for Cummins. The recent record distribution revenue, EPA approval for dual fuel X15 engines, and the US$2.1m hybrid haul truck grant have coincided with a 30 day share price return of 12.76% and a 1 year total shareholder return of 61.21%...
